&quot;It is *unlikely* that the new product launch will achieve its ambitious sales targets in the first quarter.&quot; 
&quot;*Clearly*, a well-designed marketing campaign can significantly boost brand awareness.&quot; 
&quot;*While* social media marketing is a powerful tool, traditional advertising methods like television commercials still hold value for reaching a broad audience.&quot;

&quot;*Conversely*, some customers prefer the personalized service of a physical store over the convenience of online shopping.&quot; 
&quot;*Due* to the increased popularity of online shopping, brick-and-mortar stores are facing challenges.&quot; 
&quot;*Consequently*, many stores are investing in omnichannel strategies to provide a seamless customer experience.&quot;
